WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:01.640
Previously on Good Trouble...

00:01.690 --> 00:04.100
You have massages available every day,

00:04.120 --> 00:06.840
and that is our
meditation and yoga room.

00:06.880 --> 00:08.600
You've got the nerve to bother the CEO

00:08.620 --> 00:10.280
over some stupid app idea.

00:10.290 --> 00:11.299
- Oh.
- Oh.

00:11.300 --> 00:12.879
Maybe we can just get a drink one night.

00:12.880 --> 00:14.300
- Sure.
- I still can't get over

00:14.340 --> 00:15.800
the Judge hiding his son upstairs.

00:15.840 --> 00:17.780
- You get any idea why.
- No.

00:17.800 --> 00:19.890
I hope it's enough to cover
your friends and family rate,

00:19.930 --> 00:21.160
'cause I need a lawyer.

00:21.180 --> 00:22.960
Maybe we can grab dinner some time.

00:22.980 --> 00:25.219
- I am seeing Callie.
- Does she know about me?

00:25.220 --> 00:26.700
It's not a competition.

00:26.760 --> 00:28.640
But if it was, I would
totally win, right?

00:28.690 --> 00:30.160
It's okay. We can see other people.

00:30.180 --> 00:32.460
- Kinda behind on rent.
- Can you ask Mom?

00:32.479 --> 00:33.780
I don't want their help!

00:33.820 --> 00:36.640
Davia's been hooking up with
this guy from her hometown.

00:36.680 --> 00:38.420
- He's married, Davia.
- I know.

00:38.490 --> 00:39.500
You had a kid?

00:39.520 --> 00:41.880
We lost him when he
was six, rare cancer.

00:41.900 --> 00:44.060
You told your friends I'm
clerking the Jamal case?

00:44.100 --> 00:46.080
No one's supposed to know
what cases I'm working on.

00:46.090 --> 00:47.100
You live in a theater.

00:47.120 --> 00:48.740
Do you know everyone who lives there?

00:48.760 --> 00:49.880
No, I don't.

